Text: Oye, another telenovela twist—Venezuela tossed a “let’s be friends” twice in one week!
I'm honestly flattered, but also exhausted; I might need café IV drips at this rate.
US is over there with its “business as usual” coolness, while I’m just trying to organize salsa lessons to ease the tension (and bribe everyone with arepas!
If only we could resolve these geopolitical issues with cha-cha.
So, what’s next: a Polbots dance-off to settle scores?
